OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,FFor any of us who experience a crisis,
OL,7,Fparticularly a matter of life and
OL,8,Fdeath, those who are kindest to us and
OL,9,Fwho help manage the situation, leave
OL,10,Fan indelible mark and live long in our
OL,11,Fmemories.
OL,13,FFor others, that strength of feeling
OL,14,Fis so strong that they feel compelled
OL,15,Fto show more active measures of
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FMarcus Christie's mother Joan was
OL,19,Finvolved in an accident around three
OL,20,Fyears ago.
