OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,FThe Air Ambulance was called but
OL,7,Fultimately she didn't survive.
OL,9,FMarcus was driven to show his
OL,10,Fappreciation of the professionalism
OL,11,Fand help they offered in such a
OL,12,Ftraumatic time.
OL,14,F"The Air Ambulance was there within 25
OL,15,Fminutes. I wanted to pay them back for
OL,16,Fthat service. I saw first hand how
OL,17,Famazing that service is and it's based
OL,18,Fsolely in Northern Ireland," he said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
