OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,FJoan Christie was well-known and much-
OL,7,Floved, a woman who had devoted her
OL,8,Flife to public service, a legacy not
OL,9,Flost on Marcus.
OL,11,F"She was the Lord Lieutenant for
OL,12,FCounty Antrim for about 12 years. She
OL,13,Fran herself ragged being at all the
OL,14,Fevents that she could, supporting
OL,15,Flocal initiatives and local charities.
OL,17,F"I suppose I want to keep her legacy
OL,18,Falive now. I want to keep her memory
OL,19,Falive so all the challenges I do are
OL,20,Fin her name."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
