OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,FThe challenges are extreme. To help
OL,7,FAir Ambulance NI, Marcus has climbed
OL,8,Fthe three highest peaks in the UK.
OL,10,FHe has scaled Kilimanjaro and this
OL,11,Fyear walked the length of the island
OL,12,Fof Ireland, completing the equivalent
OL,13,Fof fifteen marathons back to back.
OL,15,FI asked him about why he went to such
OL,16,Flengths to raise awareness of the work
OL,17,Fof the charity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
