OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,F"It's about doing something different
OL,7,Fand I think that's why we've done so
OL,8,Fwell raising the money because these
OL,9,Fare things that people wouldn't
OL,10,Fnormally think of doing like the walk
OL,11,Facross the country. It was just
OL,12,Fsomething totally unique."
OL,14,FIn fact, Marcus has been so successful
OL,15,Fwith his voluntary work and
OL,16,Ffundraising that he just won an award
OL,17,Ffrom Air Ambulances UK for UK Charity
OL,18,FFundraiser of the Year.
