OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: A son's tribute
OL,4,Cto mum after tragedy
OL,6,F"It was lovely to get it. It was
OL,7,Flovely to get the recognition. Not
OL,8,Fjust for me but for the charity too."
OL,10,FMarcus is passionate about the
OL,11,Fbenefits of charity work, not just for
OL,12,Fthe charity but for the individual
OL,13,Finvolved too.
OL,15,F"Volunteering is quite self-serving.
OL,16,FYou're doing good and it makes you
OL,17,Ffeel very good. There's so much good
OL,18,Fout there. I find it really rewarding
OL,19,Fand I know other people will too."
